# .pii.example — Template for personal PII patterns
#
# Copy this file to .pii and add your personal patterns:
#   cp .pii.example .pii
#
# The .pii file is in .gitignore and never committed.
# Each developer maintains their own patterns.

# Hostnames (your personal machines)
# my-hostname
# my-laptop.local

# Email addresses
# your.name@company.com

# IP addresses (your home/office network)
# 192.168.1.100

# Other personal identifiers
# your-username
# your-project-name
